<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Architecting software that ships and scales.</title>
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: dark; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { margin: 0; width: 1200px; height: 630px; overflow: hidden; background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(34,197,94,.18), transparent 34%), radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(59,130,246,.18), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #0f172a 48%, #111827 100%); color: #f8fafc; }
      .frame { display: grid; height: 100%; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; gap: 40px; padding: 56px; }
      .content { display: flex; min-width: 0; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
      .eyebrow { margin: 0 0 22px; color: rgba(226,232,240,.8); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      h1 { margin: 0; max-width: 12ch; font-size: 72px; line-height: .95; letter-spacing: -.06em; }
      .subtitle { margin: 28px 0 0; max-width: 28ch; color: rgba(226,232,240,.84); font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.35; }
      .accent { margin: 22px 0 0; max-width: 34ch; color: rgba(148,163,184,.94); font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.45; }
      .footer { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; color: rgba(148,163,184,.92); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e, #38bdf8); box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(34,197,94,.5); }
      .panel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-radius: 32px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,23,42,.8), rgba(15,23,42,.45)); padding: 28px; box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(2,6,23,.45); }
      .window,.footer-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
      .window-dots { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
      .window-dots span { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(148,163,184,.55); }
      .window-label,.stack-item span,.metric-label { color: rgba(148,163,184,.92); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .stack { display: grid; gap: 18px; }
      .stack-item { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); border-radius: 22px; background: rgba(15,23,42,.52); padding: 18px 20px; }
      .stack-item strong { display: block; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; }
      .highlights { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
      .chip { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); padding: 10px 14px; color: rgba(226,232,240,.9); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .metrics { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 16px; }
      .metric { border-radius: 22px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); padding: 18px; }
      .metric-value { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
      .cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; align-self: flex-start; margin-top: 26px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); padding: 14px 18px; color: #f8fafc; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .cta-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #22c55e); box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(56,189,248,.42); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="frame">
      <section class="content">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">VISOMI.DEV / HOME</p>
          <h1>Architecting software that ships and scales.</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Senior full-stack engineering, reusable architecture, and AI-enabled workflows.</p>
          <p class="accent">Senior engineering for products that need clear foundations and durable systems.</p>
          <div class="cta"><span class="cta-dot"></span><span>Explore the portfolio</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer"><span class="dot"></span><span>visomi.dev</span><span>engineering portfolio</span></div>
      </section>
      <aside class="panel">
        <div class="window"><div class="window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span class="window-label">preview state</span></div>
        <div class="stack"><div class="stack-item"><span>focus</span><strong>home</strong></div><div class="stack-item"><span>tone</span><strong>clear, technical, visual</strong></div></div>
        <div class="highlights"><span class="chip">Scalable platforms</span><span class="chip">AI workflows</span><span class="chip">Technical leadership</span></div>
        <div class="metrics"><div class="metric"><div class="metric-label">locale</div><div class="metric-value">EN</div></div><div class="metric"><div class="metric-label">format</div><div class="metric-value">1200x630</div></div></div>
      </aside>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
